### 请提出你的问题

 将train.py文件的train_ds, dev_ds = load_dataset("lcqmc", splits=["train", "dev"])修改为加载本地文件：
    train_ds = load_dataset(read_data, filename="../train.tsv",is_train=True,lazy=False)
    dev_ds = load_dataset(read_data, filename="../dev.tsv",is_train=True,lazy=False)

读取数据的函数如下：
def read_data(filename,is_train=True):
    with open(filename,'r',encoding='utf-8') as f:
        for line in f:
            data = line.strip().split("\t")
            # if len(data) != 3 or int(data[2]) not in [0,1]: continue
            try :
                if is_train:
                    query,title,label = data
                    yield {"query": query, "tit1e": title, "1abe1":int(label)}
                else:
                    query,title = data
                    yield {"query": query, "title": title}
            except:
                continue
报错内容如下：
query, title = example["query"], example["title"]
KeyError: 'title'

train_ds加载的数据格式和默认lcqmc相同，比如{'query': '喜欢打篮球的男生喜欢什么样的女生', 'title': '爱打篮球的男生喜欢什么样的女生', 'label': 1}，不知哪里有问题

